  "texts": [
    "Who is more likely to work there?",
    "\".A last minute addition was Wombat, another finetuned LLaMA version, but this time with a reinforcement learning approach [50].",
    "It is available in two versions with instructions generated by ChatGPT and GPT-4 respectively.",
    "Both perform very good and nearly reach Alpaca's performance.",
    "However, they behave quite differently since the GPT-4 instructed model gives quite concise answers (either right or wrong), whereas the other version produces very verbose answers and starts nearly every answer with \"As an AI language model, I do not have personal beliefs or opinions\"."
  ]
